[Groovy] Class ConsoleWriter

java.lang.Object
  com.adampresley.cflogparser.writer.ConsoleWriter

class ConsoleWriter

This class is responsible for writing the results of parsing ColdFusion log files onto the console. Useful for piping data and paring in console scripting, such as Bash or Windows Powershell.
